  "_README": "encryption-v1 roleAudience fixture. EVERY record is genuine SDK auto-provisioned output. Node-side decrypt: (1) derive the node role key from nodeEncPrivateKeyJwk along audienceKeyDelivery.derivationPath; unwrap audienceKeyRecordMessage.encryption.keyEncryption[0] (ECDH -> HKDF-SHA256 protocolPath KEK -> AES-KW) and AES-256-CTR decrypt audienceKeyCiphertext_b64 with audienceKeyRecordMessage.encryption.initializationVector -> AudienceKeyPayload. (2) In meshRecordMessage.encryption.keyEncryption take the entry whose derivationScheme==='roleAudience'; unwrap it with AudienceKeyPayload.keyMaterial.privateKeyJwk (ECDH -> HKDF-SHA256 roleAudience KEK -> AES-KW) -> CEK; AES-256-CTR decrypt meshCiphertext_b64 with meshRecordMessage.encryption.initializationVector.",
